(A) Landlord
(B) Tenant Farmer
(C) Halku’s dog
(D) None of these
Answer: (C) Halku’s dog
Explanation: Jabra was Halku’s dog.

Q.21. Munni wanted to buy a:
(A) Bangle
(B) Blanket
(C) Saree
(D) Kurti
Answer: (B) Blanket
Explanation: Munni was saving money specifically to buy a blanket for Halku to survive the cold nights.

Q.22. Who was Dhanpat Rai?
